      <title>CenterPoint Energy 飓风影响后评估债券利息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/centerpoint-energy-gauging-bond-interest-after-hurricane-impacts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，CenterPoint Energy Inc. 宣布计划出售价值 2.5 亿美元的股票，目前正在测试投资者对潜在次级债券发行的兴趣。]]></description>
